{"pageProps":{"seo":{"title":"","description":"","keywords":"","image":"https://static.pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/main_home.jpg"},"content":{"title":"","description":""},"isWorkCase":true,"workCase":{"id":1334,"name":"Miniwager","shortdescription":"Ethereum-Based Decentralized Online Gaming Platform","description":"An Ethereum-based decentralized casual gaming platform used for PvP gameplay and tournaments. Users are provided with a way to play casual games online, having the opportunity to place wagers on outcomes in ETH. The platform borrows the best features from top casual web games.","preview":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-ethereum-based-decentralized-online-gaming-platform-1920-1.jpg","preview500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-ethereum-based-decentralized-online-gaming-platform-544.jpg","preview768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-ethereum-based-decentralized-online-gaming-platform-1024.jpg","alt":"","sections":[{"acf_fc_layout":"headdescription","button_text":"Share your idea","shortdescription":"Ethereum-Based Decentralized Online Gaming Platform","description":"An Ethereum-based decentralized casual gaming platform used for PvP gameplay and tournaments","project_heading":"Project Goals","project_goal":"<p>The vision for the project was to create a platform for game developers, allowing them to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integrate payments in ETH;</li>\n<li>Reduce withdrawal fees and eliminate intermediaries;</li>\n<li>Make wagers and awards transparent using <a href=\"https://pixelplex.io/ethereum-development/\">Ethereum blockchain</a> while providing fun casual gaming experience for users.</li>\n</ul>\n","technologyheading":"Work Done","technologiestags":[{"entry":"Web GUI"},{"entry":"Server"},{"entry":"Smart Contracts"}],"tags":[{"value":"Blockchain","label":"Blockchain"},{"value":"Web","label":"Web"},{"value":"Cryptocurrency","label":"Cryptocurrency"},{"value":"Smart Contracts","label":"Smart Contracts"},{"value":"FinTech","label":"FinTech"},{"value":"Game Development","label":"Game Development"},{"value":"Blockchain Development Services","label":"Blockchain Development Services"},{"value":"Gaming Platform","label":"Gaming Platform"}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"solutions","technologies":[{"title":"Solidity","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/solidity_icon.svg","alt":"Solidity icon"}},{"title":"Truffle","image":false},{"title":"Angular","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/angularjs_icon.svg","alt":"AngularJS icon"}},{"title":"JavaScript","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/js_icon.svg","alt":"JS icon"}},{"title":"Node.js","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/nodejs_icon.svg","alt":"Node.js icon"}}],"rows":[{"title":"<h2>Solution</h2>\n","text":"<p>Miniwager is a gaming platform built on Ethereum that allows to play games in PvP and compete in tournaments to win prizes in ether.</p>\n"}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"twocolumnstext","description_top":"","slides":[{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-1-1600.jpg","alt":"Wallet interface and the list of available competitions"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-1-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-1-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-1-320.jpg"},{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-2-1600.jpg","alt":"The pool of MiniWager games"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-2-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-2-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-2-320.jpg"},{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-3-1600.jpg","alt":"Player statistics dashboard of Miniwager platform"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-3-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-3-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/miniwager-slide-3-320.jpg"}],"rows":[{"title":"<h3>Vision</h3>\n","text":"<p>Most gaming platforms do not accept cryptocurrency and have overcomplicated user funds withdrawal processes, such as the large amount of time spent on transactions and high minimum withdrawal amounts. Not to mention high commissions that players are charged by the services. Lack of transparency in game results, awards and payouts all add up to the notion of an unfair process.</p>\n"},{"title":"<h3>Solution</h3>\n","text":"<p>Users are provided with a way to play casual games online, having the opportunity to place wagers on outcomes in ETH. Players deposit their funds to dedicated Ethereum accounts (generated for each player) and can withdraw funds at their discretion. This is achieved by having the system owner’s wallet installed on the project server, and by generating addresses for all new user accounts.</p>\n<p>The platform borrows the best features from top casual web games. Therefore, MiniWager games (the likes of “Pool” and “Bubble Shooter”) are irresistible and easy to play.</p>\n"}],"title":"Details"},{"acf_fc_layout":"call_to_action","title":"Got an idea? Let’s work together","button_text":"Get in touch","background_rgb":"#64C7B4"},{"acf_fc_layout":"projectFeatures","title":"Project features","content":[{"title":"Login/registration via email/password or Facebook account","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/registration-via-email-password-facebook.svg","alt":"Blue icon of an ID"}},{"title":"Ethereum address generation for each account","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/ethereum-address-generation.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a pencil preparing a draft"}},{"title":"ETH deposits and withdrawals","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/eth-deposits-and-withdrawals.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a wallet, coins, and a banknote"}},{"title":"Smart contract-based wagers","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/smart-contract-based-wagers.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a document and a coin"}},{"title":"Casual web games","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/casual-web-games.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a game controller"}},{"title":"Awards and winnings distributed based on players’ score in games","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/awards-distributed-based-on-players-score.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a gift next to a document"}}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"relatedPosts","project":[2645,1234]}],"seoTitle":"Miniwager - Ethereum-Based Decentralized Online Gaming Platform | PixelPlex","seoDescription":"An Ethereum-based decentralized casual gaming platform used for PvP gameplay and tournaments","seoKeywords":""},"category":"","officesLocations":[{"id":86,"name":"New York, United States","city":"New York","country":"United States","address":[{"entry":"520 West 28th St."},{"entry":"Suite 31"},{"entry":"New York, NY 10001"}],"phone":{"raw":"+16464900772","formatted":"+1 646 490 0772"},"order":"1"},{"id":7479,"name":"London, United Kingdom","city":"London","country":"United Kingdom","address":[{"entry":"Kemp House,"},{"entry":"152 - 160 City Road"},{"entry":"London EC1V 2NX, UK"}],"phone":{"raw":"+442045388887","formatted":"+44 20 4538 8887"},"order":"2"},{"id":87,"name":"Pfäffikon, Switzerland","city":"Pfäffikon","country":"Switzerland","address":[{"entry":"Zentrum zum Staldenbach 11"},{"entry":"8808 Pfäffikon SZ"},{"entry":"Switzerland"}],"phone":{"raw":"+41797310314","formatted":"+41 79 731-03-14"},"order":"3"},{"id":2027,"name":"Dubai, United Arab Emirates","city":"Dubai","country":"United Arab Emirates","address":[{"entry":"Dubai Si